'''卡洛斯·安東尼奧·羅登'''（{{lang-en|Carlos Antonio Rodón}}，{{bd|1992年|12月10日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於舊金山巨人。他是[[2014年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2014年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]的選秀探花。

==職業生涯==
2014年大聯盟選秀，白襪隊在第一輪第三順位選進羅登。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140605&content_id=78406540&notebook_id=78408158&vkey=notebook_cws&c_id=cws|title=White Sox take lefty Rodon with third pick|work=Chicago White Sox|access-date=April 3, 2015|archive-date=2014-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611173049/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140605&content_id=78406540&notebook_id=78408158&vkey=notebook_cws&c_id=cws|dead-url=no}}</ref>羅登在小聯盟爬升的速度極快，不到一年的時間，他就能從高階1A直接跳級升上3A。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140820&content_id=90469334&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb|title=Top White Sox prospect Carlos Rodon allowed a run on one hit over three innings in his Triple-A debut for Charlotte - MiLB.com News - The Official Site of Minor League Baseball|work=MiLB.com|access-date=April 3, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304063640/http://www.milb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140820&content_id=90469334&fext=.jsp&vkey=news_milb&sid=milb|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===芝加哥白襪===
2015年4月21日，才簽約不滿一年的羅登就登上了大聯盟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/eye-on-baseball/25155327/white-sox-starting-carlos-rodon-like-they-started-chris-sale|title=White Sox starting Carlos Rodon like they started Chris Sale: In bullpen|publisher=CBS Sports|access-date=April 20, 2015|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304141834/http://www.cbssports.com/mlb/eye-on-baseball/25155327/white-sox-starting-carlos-rodon-like-they-started-chris-sale|dead-url=no}}</ref>當時球隊讓羅登擔任牛棚投手，他在初登板投了2.1局失2分。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Cwik|first1=Chris|title=Rodon shaky in MLB debut as White Sox lose 2-6 to Indians|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/mlb-big-league-stew/carlos-rodon-turns-in-shaky-major-league-debut-as-white-sox-lose-6-2-065358898.html|publisher=Yahoo Sports|access-date=April 22, 2015|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201044801/https://sports.yahoo.com/blogs/mlb-big-league-stew/carlos-rodon-turns-in-shaky-major-league-debut-as-white-sox-lose-6-2-065358898.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月9日，羅登完成生涯初次先發，並拿下大聯盟首勝。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2015_05_09_cinmlb_chamlb_2&mode=box |title=MLB Gameday |publisher=Major League Baseball |access-date=May 9, 2015 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304025656/http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2015_05_09_cinmlb_chamlb_2&mode=box |dead-url=no }}</ref>整季他拿下9勝6敗，防禦率3.75。

2016年7月9日，羅登因為左手腕受傷進入傷兵名單。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Merkin|first1=Scott|title=Rodon lands on DL with wrist sprain|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/188876154/carlos-rodon-wrist-injury-on-disabled-list/|publisher=MLB|access-date=July 9, 2016|archive-date=2017-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171201042436/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/188876154/carlos-rodon-wrist-injury-on-disabled-list/|dead-url=no}}</ref>該季他拿下9勝10敗，防禦率4.04。隔年他幾乎都在養傷，因此只出賽12場比賽，拿下2勝5敗。

2018年初，羅登因為肩膀受傷再次進入傷兵名單。整季他拿下6勝8敗。後來他在2019年擔任球隊的開幕戰先發投手，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/carlos-rodon-named-opening-day-starter |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2019-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190403162157/https://www.mlb.com/news/carlos-rodon-named-opening-day-starter |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過他在5月3日便因為動了湯米·約翰手術而導致球季報銷。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/carlos-rodon-needs-tommy-john-surgery-as-white-soxs-bad-fortune-with-young-starters-continues/|title=Carlos Rodon needs Tommy John surgery as White Sox's bad fortune with young starters continues|author=Matt Snyder|publisher=CBS Sports|date=2019-05-13|access-date=2019-05-21|archive-date=2019-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191030203650/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/carlos-rodon-needs-tommy-john-surgery-as-white-soxs-bad-fortune-with-young-starters-continues/|dead-url=no}}</ref>該年他只拿下3勝2敗，送出46次三振。

2020年，羅登僅出賽4場比賽，拿下2敗，防禦率高達8.22。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlb.com/player/carlos-rodon-607074 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2021-06-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210614042808/https://www.mlb.com/player/carlos-rodon-607074 |dead-url=no }}</ref>他在12月2日接獲球隊的不續約通知，<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/12/white-sox-non-tender-nomar-mazara-carlos-rodon.html |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128113623/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2020/12/white-sox-non-tender-nomar-mazara-carlos-rodon.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>不過後來又在隔年1月30日與球隊簽下1年300萬美元的合約。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/white-sox/2021/2/1/22261121/white-sox-announce-one-year-deal-with-left-hander-carlos-rodon |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-03-03 |archive-date=2021-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210221230624/https://chicago.suntimes.com/white-sox/2021/2/1/22261121/white-sox-announce-one-year-deal-with-left-hander-carlos-rodon |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2021年4月14日，羅登在面對印地安人時，連續解決25名打者。雖然對第26名打者[[羅伯托·培瑞茲|羅伯托·培瑞茲]]投出觸身球錯失完全比賽，不過他隨後又解決後面兩位打者，投出2021年球季大聯盟第二場的無安打比賽。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/gameday/indians-vs-white-sox/2021/04/14/634516#game_state=final,game_tab=box,game=634516|title=White Sox 8, Indians 0, Wednesday, April 14, 2021|website=MLB.com|access-date=April 14, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420044351/https://www.mlb.com/gameday/indians-vs-white-sox/2021/04/14/634516#game_state=final,game_tab=box,game=634516|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nbcsports.com/chicago/white-sox/white-sox-lefty-carlos-rodon-throws-no-hitter-teams-20th|title=Carlos Rodón throws 20th no-hitter in Sox history|website=NBC Sports Chicago|last=Duber|first=Vinnie|date=April 14, 2021|access-date=April 14, 2021|archive-date=2021-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210416181910/https://www.nbcsports.com/chicago/white-sox/white-sox-lefty-carlos-rodon-throws-no-hitter-teams-20th|dead-url=no}}</ref>
